org.bytedeco.javacpp

Class avdevice.AVDeviceCapabilitiesQuery

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bytedeco.javacpp.Pointer
      • org.bytedeco.javacpp.avdevice.AVDeviceCapabilitiesQuery
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable
    Enclosing class:
    avdevice

    public static class avdevice.AVDeviceCapabilitiesQuery
extends org.bytedeco.javacpp.Pointer
    Structure describes device capabilities. It is used by devices in conjunction with av_device_capabilities AVOption table to implement capabilities probing API based on AVOption API. Should not be used directly.
